title: The Best of Jesse Winchester (1989, Bearsville) [flac]
description:
The Best of Jesse Winchester (1985, Bearsville)

The great Jesse Winchester passed away today, April 11, 2014.
The world has lost a great singer-songwriter and a forgiving and gentle soul.
